Job Description
Share
Maintain the highest possible hygiene and maintenance standards. Ensure the highest degree in applied hygiene and food safety as per the, HACCP guidelines to ensure that the food served to the Guest is of highest quality and standard
Ensure that all dishes leaving the kitchen are of appropriate portion and presented as per recipes and presentation standards set by the Hotel
Work in close cooperation with all other key departments in the Hotel to ensure a smooth operation
Attend daily banquet operational meetings and Banquets events coordinators meeting
Prepare all Oriental food for all banquet events and restaurants with the help of junior staff and help in serving for banquet functions as per Hotel standards
Constantly check for freshness, presentations and temperature of oriental food served in restaurants or functions
Control the food cost by preparing / reviewing all store requisitions and direct purchases and ensure the accurate delivery of goods in order to achieve the budgeted profitability
Attend required meetings and conduct daily briefings with your team members ensuring efficient communication, to run your kitchen smoothly
attractive salary and benefits
